your-bot-project/
│
├─ bot.py                 # Main bot file, loads all cogs
├─ requirements.txt       # Python dependencies
├─ README.md              # Optional
│
├─ cogs/                  # All commands live here
│   ├─ __init__.py        # Makes 'cogs' a Python package (required)
│   ├─ ping.py            # Ping command
│   ├─ echo.py            # Echo command
│   └─ purge.py           # Purge command
│
└─ .env (optional)        # Environment variable file if not using Railway shared variables
